{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantProtocol\/getNormalForm()"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Gets a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance that has the same value as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"text":" and is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"trusted to be in normal form."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/variantprotocol\/getnormalform()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"getNormalForm()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getNormalForm"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"VariantRef","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"modules":[{"name":"GLib"}],"extendedModule":"GLib","externalID":"s:4GLib15VariantProtocolPAAE13getNormalFormAA0B3RefVSgyF"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"getNormalForm"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV","text":"VariantRef","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"!","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" is already trusted to be in normal form then a new"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reference to "},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is returned."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"text":" is not already trusted, then it is scanned to check if it","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is in normal form.  If it is found to be in normal form then it is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"marked as trusted and a new reference to it is returned.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"type":"text","text":" is found not to be in normal form then a new trusted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","isActive":true},{"text":" is created with the same value as ","type":"text"},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". The non-normal parts of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be replaced with default values which are guaranteed to be in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"normal form."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It makes sense to call this function if you’ve received "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","isActive":true},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"data from untrusted sources and you want to ensure your serialized"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"output is definitely in normal form."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"value"},{"text":" is already in normal form, a new reference will be returned","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(which will be floating if ","type":"text"},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is floating). If it is not in normal form,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the newly created "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" will be returned with a single non-floating","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"reference. Typically, "},{"code":"g_variant_take_ref()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" should be called on the return","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"value from this function to guarantee ownership of a single non-floating"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"reference to it.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantProtocol"]]},"references":{"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/Variant":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variant","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","kind":"symbol","title":"Variant","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Variant","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Variant","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"code":"GVariant","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is a variant datatype; it can contain one or more values","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"along with information about the type of the values.","type":"text"}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/VariantRef":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantRef"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantRef","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantRef"}],"title":"VariantRef","url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variantref","abstract":[{"code":"GVariant","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is a variant datatype; it can contain one or more values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"along with information about the type of the values."}]},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/VariantProtocol":{"title":"VariantProtocol","abstract":[{"code":"GVariant","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is a variant datatype; it can contain one or more values","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"along with information about the type of the values.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantProtocol"}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variantprotocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"VariantProtocol"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantProtocol","role":"symbol"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib/VariantProtocol/getNormalForm()":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/VariantProtocol\/getNormalForm()","role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Gets a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/Variant","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" instance that has the same value as "},{"code":"value","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"trusted to be in normal form."}],"url":"\/documentation\/glib\/variantprotocol\/getnormalform()","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"getNormalForm","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"() -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"VariantRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:4GLib10VariantRefV"},{"kind":"text","text":"!"}],"title":"getNormalForm()"},"doc://GLib/documentation/GLib":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","title":"GLib","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/glib"}}}